{"lemma":"نَجْدُ","slug":"نَجْدُ","root":"ن.ج.د","root_slug":"ن-ج-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ج-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":9,"pos_tags":["name","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39384","n39385","n39386","n39387","n39388"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"highland, plateau"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Najd, the central region of Saudi Arabia"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to help, aid, assist, support"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stand by someone"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to furnish"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to upholster"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to comb, to card (cotton)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sweat"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be brave"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39384","headword_ar":"نَجْدٌ","root":"njd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"High,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated, land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, and rugged, and elevated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high, table-land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stony and rugged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, elevated land, like a mountain, standing over against one and intercepting his view of what is behind it, but not very high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thus called: (L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anojudN","text_ar":"اَنْجُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) a pl. of pauc., (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anojaAdN","text_ar":"اَنْجَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) [also a pl. of pauc.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nijaAdN","text_ar":"نِجَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujuwdN","text_ar":"نُجُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujudN","text_ar":"نُجُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAar, L, K;) and pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujuwdN","text_ar":"نُجُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anojidapN","text_ar":"اَنْجِدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [another pl. of pauc.;] (S, K;) or this is a mistake, and it is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nijaAdN","text_ar":"نِجَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomirapN","text_ar":"اَحْمِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaArN","text_ar":"حِمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or it is a pl. deviating from common rule. (IB, L.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uEolu haAtiyka Aln~ijaAda","text_ar":"اُعْلُ هَاتِيكَ النِّجَادَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ascend thou these high lands;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haA*aAka Aln~ijaAda","text_ar":"هَاذَاكَ النِّجَادَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this high land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"making it singular. (L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K, &c.,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najudN","text_ar":"نَجُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) the latter of the dial. of Hudheyl, (Akh,) of the masc. gender, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The high land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a division of the country of the Arabs; opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algaworu","text_ar":"الغَوْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or the low country,] i. e., Tihámeh;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all the high land from Tihámeh to the land of El-'Irák;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above it are Tihámeh and El-Yemen, and below it El-'Irák and Esh-Shám;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it begins, towards El-Hijáz, at Dhát-'Irk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and ends at Sawád of El-'Irák,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence it is said to form no part of El-Hijáz: (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it comprises all that is beyond the moat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fosse, which Kisrà made to the Sawád of El-'Irák until one inclines to the Harrah"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHar~ap","text_ar":"الحَرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he is in El-Hijáz;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Báhilee, T, L, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and it extends to the east of El-Ghowr,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Ghór;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is all the tract of which the torrents flow westwards: Tihámeh extends from Dhát-'Irk to the distance of two days' journey beyond Mekkeh: the tract beyond this, westward, is Ghowr, or Ghór; and beyond this, southwards, is Es-Saráh, as far as the frontiers of El-Yemen: (El-Báhilee, L:) or, as the Arabs of the desert have been heard to say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the country which one enters when, journeying upwards, he leaves behind him 'Ijliz, which is above El-Karyateyn, and which he quits when he descends from the mountain-roads of Dhát- 'Irk, where he enters Tihámeh, and when he meets with the stony tracts termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiraAr","text_ar":"حِرَار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in Nejd, where El-Hijáz commences:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the high country from Batn-er-Rummeh to the mountain-roads of Dhát-'Irk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the country from El-'Odheyb to Dhát-'Irk, and to El-Yemámeh, and to El-Yemen, and to the two mountains of Teiyi, and from El-Mirbed to Wejreh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Dhât-'Irk is the beginning of Tihámeh, extending to the sea and Juddeh: El-Medeeneh is not of Tihámeh nor of Nejd, but of El-Hijáz, higher than El-Ghowr, or El-Ghór, and lower than Nejd. (IAar, L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An elevated road:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an elevated and conspicuous road."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road in a mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) [Hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~aAEu","text_ar":"طَلَّاعُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^anojudi","text_ar":"الاَنْجُدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. below, and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TlE","text_ar":"طلع"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hadayonaAhu","text_ar":"هَدَيْنَاهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ajodayoni","text_ar":"النَّجْدَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Kur, xc. 10]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have shown him the two ways;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the way of good and that of evil: (Beyd, Jel, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two conspicuous ways:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) ―         -b5-  or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have given him the two breasts;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Beyd, L;) for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a woman's breast;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K;) the belly beneath it being like the [country called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gawor","text_ar":"غَوْر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amaA wanajodayohaA","text_ar":"اَمَا وَنَجْدَيْهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA faEalota *`lika","text_ar":"مَا فَعَلْتَ ذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Now, by her two breasts, didst thou not that?"},{"kind":"text","text":"A form of oath of the Arabs. (MF.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAjidN","text_ar":"نَاجِدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"A thing, or an affair,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparent, manifest, plain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evident."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa Tal~aAEu A^anojudK","text_ar":"هُوَ طَلَّاعُ اَنْجُدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tl~AE A^anojidapK","text_ar":"طلّاع اَنْجِدَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tl~AE nijaAdK","text_ar":"طلّاع نِجَادٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^anojudi","text_ar":"الاَنْجُدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TlE","text_ar":"طلع"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlnijaAdi","text_ar":"النِجَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is one who surmounts difficult affairs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is one who manages affairs thoroughly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and masters them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is a man expert in affairs, who surmounts and masters them by his knowledge and experience and excellent judgment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who aims at lofty things:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TlE","text_ar":"طلع"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is one who rises to eminences,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to lofty things"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumstances,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the means of attaining such things:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~aAEu Alv~anaAyaA","text_ar":"طَلَّاعُ الثَّنَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TlE","text_ar":"طلع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najidN","text_ar":"نَجِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munaAjidN","text_ar":"مُنَاجِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujuwdN","text_ar":"نُجُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, S, L, K) and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nijaAdN","text_ar":"نِجَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) which signify The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"articles of household farniture and the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mtAE","text_ar":"متاع"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which a house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"byt","text_ar":"بيت"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is ornamented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decorated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, S, L;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carpets and beds"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other things that are spread, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pillows, used for that purpose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cloths"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stuffs used for this purpose, with which the walls are hung, and which are spread;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curtains which are hung upon the walls:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anojaAdN","text_ar":"اَنْجَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"household furniture, consisting of such things as are spread, and pillows, and curtains."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or an"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"guide of the way. (L, K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujudN","text_ar":"نُجُدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place in which are no trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of tree resembling the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uborum","text_ar":"شُبْرُم"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its colour and manner of growth and its thorns."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","Msb","K","TA","Akh","As","ISk","Beyd","Jel","A"]},{"entry_id":"n39385","headword_ar":"نَجَدٌ","root":"njd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sweat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sorrow, grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anxiety, &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ajadaAtu","text_ar":"النَّجَدَاتُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain sect of the Khárijees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those called the Harooreeyeh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the companions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"followers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Nejdeh Ibn-'Ámir"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Harooree"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Hanafee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Benoo-Haneefeh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also called"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ajodiy~apu","text_ar":"النَّجْدِيَّةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2768}],"source_refs":["S","L","K"]},{"entry_id":"n39386","headword_ar":"نَجُدٌ","root":"njd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naji*N","text_ar":"نَجِذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n39387","headword_ar":"نَجِدٌ","root":"njd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najudN","text_ar":"نَجُدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najiydN","text_ar":"نَجِيدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, L, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K) A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"courageous"},{"kind":"text","text":"man, (S, M, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vigorous and effective, in those affairs which others lack power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability to accomplish:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"courageous and strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very valiant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick in assenting to that which he is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"invited to do, whether it be good"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L:) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najudN","text_ar":"نَجُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anojaAdN","text_ar":"اَنْجَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayoqaAZN","text_ar":"اَيْقَاظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaquZN","text_ar":"يَقُظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L;) or this is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najidN","text_ar":"نَجِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Sb, M, L;) and not of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najiydN","text_ar":"نَجِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, L:) the pl. of this last is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujudN","text_ar":"نُجُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujadaA='u","text_ar":"نُجَدَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, L.) ―         -b2-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ajiydu","text_ar":"النَّجِيدُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so called because of his courage. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najidN fiY AlHaAjapi","text_ar":"نَجِدٌ فِى الحَاجَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick in accomplishing that which is wanted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"needed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najidN","text_ar":"نَجِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manojuwdN","text_ar":"مَنْجُودٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najiydN","text_ar":"نَجِيدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAjidN","text_ar":"نَاجِدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which last the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is perhaps inserted by poetic licence, (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sweating, by reason of work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sorrow, grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anxiety, &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manojuwdN","text_ar":"مَنْجُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","L","K","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n39388","headword_ar":"نُجُدٌ","root":"njd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najodN","text_ar":"نَجْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}